{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0ae1799078","title":"“应该打开人事档案”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"715aeb39f4","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"0ae1799078"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"17d60aee8d","name":"秦培元"},{"id":"4413d0090a","name":"洪祖猷"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"},{"id":"a13aecd501","name":"袁焕麟"},{"id":"d05847b78e","name":"孙增垣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b3fe1f9b92","type":"title","text":"“应该打开人事档案”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"aa057ff84c","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院秦培元孙增垣洪祖猷袁焕麟","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"f4b67d55bb","type":"paragraph","text":"秦培元说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"ce9eb65476","type":"paragraph","text":"“人事科是独立王国，坚决反对人事部门的独立王国。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"ae4d6cd720","type":"paragraph","text":"“生产部门只看我们的人事档案决定实习地点和工作地点，对同学自尊心损害很大，因此，应该打开人事档案。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"ca36a0c8e4","type":"paragraph","text":"“人事部门尽是党团员，有顾虑不敢提意见”，“所以要动员人事部门的职员们，先生们……起来吧，不要怕打碎自己的饭碗！”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"237d6e978f","type":"paragraph","text":"“毕业分配不要这样神秘，公开大家讨论，不允许存在过去鬼鬼祟祟的作法”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"b0c1b8d851","type":"paragraph","text":"“服从组织分配，真是残酷，一个人一生的事业就由上级决定了。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"f078cab325","type":"paragraph","text":"孙增垣说：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"c2a63def4a","type":"paragraph","text":"“有些保密是无知，把不该保密的也保密了，如100万分之一的地质图应该是普及人民群众的通俗读物。有些保密是家丑不可外扬，怕别人知道了，使人不知虚实。”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"e857d2b616","type":"paragraph","text":"洪祖猷说：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"3fc2fe37bc","type":"paragraph","text":"“班上党员骑在人民头上，是流氓，国民党作风。我不知道什么叫特务，如果是指负有特殊任务时，那么我们的人事公安的工作方法，内容和过去国民党都相似，只不过工作范围不同，所以叫特务机关也可以。人事部门的档案里就是把我们平时讲的话都放进去。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"6811ecfc9b","type":"paragraph","text":"袁焕麟要求取消档案材料，说：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"eb5d314614","type":"paragraph","text":"“档案里填了一些自己都不知的东西，必不可免的会有不是事实的。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"},{"id":"bf2a25bf17","type":"paragraph","text":"“人事科看人的档案材料，造成贼的儿子而一定是贼。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078"}],"page":{"id":"22c8772683","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"0ae1799078","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}